/******************************************************************************    
** Name:     UPS_SIT_GetPaymentFile    
** Short Desc:   Get All Client and PIF Accounts associated to the Client.     
**    
** Full Description : Get All Client and PIF Accounts associated to the Client.   
**            
**    
** Sample Call    
  Declare @status int    
        EXEC UPS_SIT_GetPaymentFile  123    
